                                <h1 class="articleHeadline">Mark Twain&#x2019;s Autobiography Flying Off the Shelves</h1>
                                <h6 class="byline">By <a href="http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/b/julie_bosman/index.html?inline=nyt-per" title="More Articles by Julie Bosman" class="meta-per">JULIE BOSMAN</a></h6>
                                <h6 class="dateline">Published: November 19, 2010</h6>
