                                <div class="articleBody">
                                    <p>
                                        When editors at the University of California Press pondered the possible demand for &#x201C;Autobiography of <a href="http://topics.nytimes.com/top/reference/timestopics/people/c/samuel_langhorne_clemens/index.html?inline=nyt-per"
                                            title="More articles about Samuel Langhorne Clemens." class="meta-per">Mark Twain</a>,&#x201D; a $35, four-pound, 500,000-word doorstopper of <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2010/07/10/books/10twain.html?_r=1"
                                            title="Times article on the memoir.">a memoir</a>, they kept their expectations modest with a planned print run of 7,500 copies. </p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="articleInline runaroundLeft">
                                    <div class="inlineImage module">
                                        <div class="image">
                                            <div class="icon enlargeThis"><a href="javascript:pop_me_up2(&apos;https://www.nytimes.com/imagepages/2010/11/20/TWAIN.html&apos;,&apos;TWAIN_html&apos;,&apos;width=720,height=586,scrollbars=yes,toolbars=no,resizable=yes&apos;)">Enlarge This Image</a></div>
                                            <a href="javascript:pop_me_up2(&apos;https://www.nytimes.com/imagepages/2010/11/20/TWAIN.html&apos;,&apos;TWAIN_html&apos;,&apos;width=720,height=586,scrollbars=yes,toolbars=no,resizable=yes&apos;)">
				<img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2010/11/20/arts/TWAIN/TWAIN-articleInline.jpg" width="190" height="152" alt="">
					</a>
                                        </div>
                                        <h6 class="credit">Mark Twain Project, the Bancroft Library</h6>
                                        <p class="caption">Mark Twain </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="columnGroup doubleRule">
                                        <h3 class="sectionHeader">Related</h3>
                                        <ul class="headlinesOnly multiline flush">
                                            <li>
                                                <h6><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/19/books/review/Keillor-t.html?ref=books">
                                    Sunday Book Review: &#x2018;Autobiography of Mark Twain: Volume 1&#x2019;</a> (December 19, 2010)
                                                </h6>
                                            </li>
                                            <p><a href="http://www.thisismarktwain.com/" target="_blank">The Book&#x2019;s Web Site</a></p>
                                            <li>
                                                <h6><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2010/07/10/books/10btwain.html?ref=books">
                                    Excerpts From the &#x2018;Autobiography of Mark Twain&#x2019;</a> (July 10, 2010)
                                                </h6>
                                            </li>
                                            <li>
                                                <h6><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2010/07/10/books/10twain.html?ref=books">
                                    Dead for a Century, Twain Says What He Meant</a> (July 10, 2010)
                                                </h6>
                                            </li>
